listing.description:
Unique three-bedroom end of terrace property for sale located off Tullow Road in good condition. The property occupies a corner plot and has the benefit of the one largest gardens in the estate. The front offers parking for two cars with the potential for an extension to the rear or side of the property subject to the relevant planning permission.

Situated within minutes of the Town Centre and all local amenities such as shops and schools, the property is within minutes of major transport links such as the N7/M9. The property on the ground floor comprises a sitting room, downstairs WC, and kitchen with a patio door to an enclosed garden. Upstairs comprises the master bedroom, a single room to the front and a double room to the back, and a family bathroom. 

Ideal for FT buyers and investors alike. Viewing is highly recommended and through appointment only. 

ACCOMMODATION: 
Entrance Hallway: 1.859m x 3.980m Tiled Flooring, Carpet, Guest WC 
Lounge: 33.786m X 3.648m Laminate Flooring, Gas Fire, Curtains. 
Kitchen 5.774m x 2.926m Tiled  Flooring, tiled splashback, Fitted Kitchen Units, White Goods, Sliding Glass Door to Back Garden 
Bathroom: 2.176 x 1.706 Lino flooring, WC, WHB, Bath, tiled walls
Bedroom 1: 2.430m x 2.387m Double Bedroom to Rear, Voile Curtains, carpet flooring, Curtain 
Bedroom 2: Single Bedroom to Front, Carpet, Curtain Voiles, Curtain, Built-in Wardrobe 
Bedroom 3: 3.636m x 3.250m Double Bedroom to Front, laminate floorin, Radiators, Curtain Voile, Curtain
Disclaimer: The above particulars are issued by Maher Property Advisors on the understanding that all negotiations are conducted through them. Please note that we have not tested any apparatus, fixtures, fittings, or services. Interested parties must undertake their own investigation into the working order of these items. All measurements are approximate and photographs provided for guidance only.
